Subject: easycap: include linux/smp_lock.h for BKL
Patch-mainline: Submitted Nov 22, 2010

 Commit 451a3c24b013 removed smp_lock.h from easycap.h because the BKL wasn't
 used in that file. This patch re-adds it to easycap_main.c, where the BKL
 is actually used.

Signed-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>
